{"tid":2215251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（美國隊長）冰島冰川融化 令76年前墜毀美軍轟炸機重見天日","createTime":"2020-09-24T01:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:10:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d211a2a187c74e68cad32504094d5188eaa0b6ca","tid":2215251,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"全球氣候暖化，令不少冰川融化，想不到卻令美國二戰時期一架墜落的B-17空中堡壘轟炸機（B-17 flying fortress）殘骸可以重見天日。轟炸機在76年前於冰島南部的埃亞菲亞德拉冰川（Eyjafjallajokull glacier）墜機，機身被冰川埋沒，直至最近冰川因氣候暖化融解，戰機殘骸重現人間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200924/LAEJXT6MRBFVFK4PGX477XPSNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200924%2FLAEJXT6MRBFVFK4PGX477XPSNI%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=282edba0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200924%2FLAEJXT6MRBFVFK4PGX477XPSNI%2F&h=064ee048\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200924/LAEJXT6MRBFVFK4PGX477XPSNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*Om_86A-t5HruezHx.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F640%2F0%2AOm_86A-t5HruezHx.jpeg&h=06e20b27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b31b0f68ff9cb9dd5dd61a5fc4cf33e718c3f823","tid":2215251,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dt0tD_-VYAAWva-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDt0tD_-VYAAWva-.jpg&h=49c23625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"640222994090d213adeab2899f325022206934c8","tid":2215251,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/MeatyIlliterateDuck-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FMeaty